author: Dan Wootton
title: Coronavirus: China’s wetmarkets should be banned
description: China’s cruel wet markets that caused coronavirus and brought the world to its knees should be banned
content:
Warning: Graphic content
Even for a carnivore like me, the images are gruesome and disgusting enough to consider whether I’ll eat meat again.
